cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CR 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with challenges in video-based face recognition and proposes a method to measure similarity using deep face features. 
2. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also likely as the paper deals with processing videos and selecting frames based on pose diversity. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses K-means clustering to select frames and deep features to measure similarity. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper proposes a method to improve the descriptiveness of deep features using geometric cues. 
5. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is a less likely category as the paper does not deal with cryptography or security, but it is still possible as the paper deals with face recognition which has applications in security systems.
